### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### operations.http — Operations Graph Contract (ADR-040)
### Validates the operations graph endpoint for system introspection.
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Authenticate
# @name login
POST {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{$dotenv ADMIN_EMAIL}}",
  "password": "{{$dotenv ADMIN_PASSWORD}}"
}

?? status == 200

###

### Operations Graph — System Topology
# @name operationsGraph
GET {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/api/v1/operations/graph
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.token}}

?? status == 200


